cs.DC, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.LG, cs.NE 

This paper focuses on resource management for virtual machines in data centers, which falls under the category of Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC). The paper also proposes an adaptive system that uses machine learning techniques, which suggests the involvement of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). The system is designed to manage adaptations, which implies the involvement of control systems (cs.SY). The paper also mentions the use of transfer learning, which is a popular technique in machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper mentions the use of contextual bandits, which is a type of reinforcement learning, and thus Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) could also be a possible category.
